Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, irreplaceable soul brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond to my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Formation Liberator, Igraine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quintet Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He blocked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now only 1 more damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aich's gonna win this, \Nno doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to release Kai from that darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks won't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I've surpassed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:00:59.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is \Ngoing to swallow you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, this whole world\Nwill belong to our Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have the power of Link Joker,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong you've gotten, Kai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win and break you free \Nof that Reversed spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...our...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:24.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Bond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Radiate noble power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn it into a universal bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crossbreak ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liberator of Bonds, Gancelot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets +10000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escrad, Flame of Victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Bruno get +5000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With his Quintet Wall, he did a break ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and even a crossbreak ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But two units are locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so Sendou can only attack twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock! Link Joker! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi can still beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to throw everything \NI've got at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escrad attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got one attack left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame of Victory boosts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,an attack from Gancelot Zenith!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bond between souls \Nthat's deeper than blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For dreams! For justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Resonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gancelot Zenith's Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escrad goes to the bottom of my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I superior call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phallon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He switched out a unit after it attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can not only attack once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he powers up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Second check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give all of the effects to Phallon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phallon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:49.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't even do 1 damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've figured there'd \Nbe two perfect guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over. If Kai can protect himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then so can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...final fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't able to win this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That shows your true ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength that lit a fire under me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that changed my principles and \Nmade me choose Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've surpassed that strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai, you're possessed by Link Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bring you to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of hearing those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat you this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar that shatters both good and evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fangs that cut through light and darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute dragon, everything \Ngrovels before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:17.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Star-vader, Chaos Breaker Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the rear-guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Breaker gets +10000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanthanum gets +2000 power for \Nevery unit that was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be locked by me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lock Phallon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Lanthanum's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanthanum moves up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He guarded against the first attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanthanum boosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chaos Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, Sword Formation Liberator, Igraine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quintet Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That's 25000 total shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his second Quintet Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:38.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Brother Aichi for you! \NNow he's got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no wall that \Ncannot be broken through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the drive trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Second check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give +5000 power to Chaos Breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and heal 1 damage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 25000 Quintet Wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was broken through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet! Damage trigger, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Aichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a perfect fight for Brother Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:30.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Aichi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've surpassed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this deck anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker's power has become my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Reverse begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw away everything \Nto obtain this strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different, Aichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to help friends \Nwho have become enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and save a world that's already \Nstarting to become Reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you're carrying everything on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One threw away everything; \Nthe other took on the burden of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what separates us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was obsessed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's over, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you become Reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't become everyone's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to turn you back to normal, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Aichi Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To resist being Reversed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to stop the Reverse process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can withstand Link Joker's locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you struggle, \Nthe more you'll suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender to the darkness that's welling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that and it'll be much easier on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Resisting being Reversed will only cause
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,your soul to be worn away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and your strength to be sapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, what you have waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is the worst result ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Souryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping Sendou... so don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Sendou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your Psyqualia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psyqualia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:48.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop the Reverse \Nprocess with my power alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it can be stopped or not
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,depends on you, Aichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your feelings strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something that you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we were in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This may seem sudden, but your world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is going to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the Takuto you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:10.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like me, but there's \Nanother consciousness inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A clan I knew nothing about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,sealed me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it swallowed up the planet Cray
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and is now trying to claim this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you're saying \Nthe person who saved Aichi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was the real Takuto, \Nwho's been sealed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Takuto, who no longer has \Na physical body in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,can only be seen by someone \Nwho possesses Psyqualia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Psyqualia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you say it, I believe it, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto is right about there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you help Takuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when I was \Nfighting a Reversed fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, I heard Takuto's voice calling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the voice's directions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and came to the real Takuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in a state of paralysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,sealed away on the planet Cray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to foil Link Joker's ambitions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and bring Cray back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this world too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already mostly been \Nswallowed up by Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much time is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only remaining measure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is to defeat Link Joker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the cause of all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, there's no guarantee that Cray \Nor this world will return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the only thing \Nwe can pin our hopes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Takuto and I are going \Nin there to beat Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it exhausted like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no shape to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou, I think you can hear him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll tell everyone else what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Aichi Sendou,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you miraculously stopped the Reverse process
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,with the power of your strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the price you've paid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is major damage to your body and psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you to fight."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lay it on the line, Aichi Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even fighting right now \Nwould put your life in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Reverse process was \Nstopped only temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fight again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the power that was held back \Ngets released all at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the force of it \Nattacking your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely do not fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm going to save Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Takuto and I are going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you,\N take care of Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to beat Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to defeat Link Joker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So watch over Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. You can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jillian... Sharlene...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect Sendou, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need it so that Takuto Tatsunagi \Ncan appear, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto Tatsunagi should be \Nable to appear with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:30.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. This works fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be sure to return it, Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better! \NYou'd better give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:43.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai... I'm going to save Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Sendou...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're deeply wounded, in mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it. Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon... Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Two Leons!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:24.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Two Leons
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. Leon Souryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give you the \Nred-carpet treatment.